    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "But I scattered them - Rather, \"And I will scatter them.\" The saying continues what God had said that he had said, and which had come to pass. Among all nations whom they knew not. So God had repeatedly said by Jeremiah, \"I will cast you out of this land into a land that ye know not, ye nor your fathers; where I will not show you favor\" (",
