        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "). This was the aggravation of the original woe in the law: \"The Lord shall bring a nation against thee from far, from the end of the earth, a nation whose tongue thou shalt not understand, a nation of fierce countenance\" ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
