        "text": "Deuteronomy 28:49-50",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". There was no mitigation of suffering, when the common bond between man and man, mutual speech, was wanting.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "That no man passed through nor returned - Literally, \"from passer through and from returner;\" as in the prophecy of Alexander's march and return, \"because of him that passeth by and of him that returneth\" Zechariah 9:8; and of Seir God saith, \"I will cut off from him, passer-through and returner\" . As we say, there shall be no traffic more through her.",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "That no man passed through nor returned - Literally, \"from passer through and from returner;\" as in the prophecy of Alexander's march and return, \"because of him that passeth by and of him that returneth\" ",
