      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "bld",
        "text": "But I scattered them; ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " when they had so provoked me, I cast them out of their habitations, pursued them with the tempest of wrath that scattered them as I threatened. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
        "text": "",
